data.description: Meticulously Maintained * You Will Appreciate the Pride of Ownership in This Lovely 2-story Home in Live Oak Bridlewood Subdivision w/ an Outstanding Park, Sports Courts, a Kids Splash Pool & More Features an Open Floor Plan ~ With 5 Bedrooms & 3 Full Baths This Spacious Home Features a Grand Entry-Way w/Diamond-Cut Tile ~ Relax in the Spacious Family Room Featuring Hard Wood Floors ~ Kitchen with Elegant Granite Counter Tops ~ Stainless Appliances ~ Gorgeous Cabinets ~ Upstairs You Will Find The Large Primary Suite w/ Huge Walk-In Closet, Separate Garden Tub & Shower ~ Oversized Game Room/Additional Living space Upstairs along with 3 Additional Bedrooms ~ Beneficial Secondary Bedroom Downstairs w/ Access to Full Bath ~ Relax on your Custom Deck w/Built in Hot Tub and Additional Covered Patio/Uncovered Patio ~ Water Softener ~ Sprinkler System ~ Gutters ~ Quiet Culdesac Setting ~ Don't Miss Out on Seeing This One!
